Bootylicious actress Phindile Gwala was allegedly dumped by Isibaya actress Jessica Nkosi as a friend over the hard cash lunch incident in Sandton. The details about the collapse of the two TV beauties' friendship was revealed by Nkosi's public relations agency boss Sarit Tomlinson of Capacity Relations last week. This, Tomlinson said, was because Gwala, who resigned from SABC drama Muvhango in July, had ambushed Nkosi to pose for pictures with a dish full of money in which she was showed in the company of two other men indulging in the hard cash. TO READ THE FULL STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD AT YOUR NEAREST STORE